name: Avaxtars
public_notice: The smart-contract owner can mint new tokens, please proceed with caution.

description.en: AVXT Token is a crypto-asset that was generated on Avalanche Blockchain Platform using ERC-20 Token standard. The AVXT token is a utility token generated by farming NFTs, used to accelerate NFT farming, trading Boxes, items and newly generated Gen2 NFTs.
